Heal I Focus works for<br>
Minor Heal<br>
Light Heal<br>
Healing<br>
<br>
Heal 2 Focus works for<br>
Greater Healing<br>
<br>
Heal 3 Focus works for<br>
Superior Heal<br>
Chloroblast<br>
Nature's Touch<br>
<br>
Heal 2 and Mana Preservation 2 Focus items works very well for a druid from Lvl 29 to 50.  HP/Mana ratio on Greater Heal with those items better than Superior Heal without Heal 3 and<br>
Mana Preserv 3.<br>
<br>
(270/150) *1.1*1.1= 2.18 hp/mana<br>
vs.<br>
(525/250)= 2.1 hp/mana<br>
